Get clinical data by attribute study ID and sample ID

get_clinical_by_patient.Rd

Get clinical data by attribute study ID and sample ID

get_clinical_by_patient(
  study_id = NULL,
  sample_id = NULL,
  clinical_attribute = "CANCER_TYPE"
)

Arguments

study_id

study ID
sample_id

a single tumor sample ID
clinical_attribute

a specific clinical attribute

Value

a dataframe of a specific clinical attribute

Examples

get_cbioportal_db('public')
get_clinical_by_patient(study_id = "acc_tcga", sample_id = "TCGA-OR-A5J2-01",
 clinical_attribute = "CANCER_TYPE")
